<item>
            <title>[LU-754] connetathon got permission deny on NFS v4 over lustre</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-754</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With exports option &quot;all_squash&quot;,running connectathon on NFS4 client over lustre, got permission deny error. With option &quot;no_root_squash&quot; option, this test can pass.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e326bfbe-f46e-11e0-908b-52540025f9af&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/e326bfbe-f46e-11e0-908b-52540025f9af&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;it looks like the same issue as &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-271&quot; title=&quot;NFS4 over lustre open permission check failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-271&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-271&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
